#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:157
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "NOTE: You must have a file open before you can create a new institution. "
#| "If you do not have an existing file, you will need to create a <link "
#| "linkend=\"firsttime.3\">new file</link>."
msgid ""
"You must have a file open before you can create a new institution. If you do "
"not have an existing file, you will need to <link linkend=\"firsttime.newfile"
"\">create one</link>."
msgstr ""
"BILJEŠKA: Morate imati otvorenu datoteku prije nego što možete napraviti "
"novu instituciju. Ukoliko nemate postojuću datoteku, morate kreirati <link "
"linkend=\"firsttime.3\">novu datoteku</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-institutions.docbook:163
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Only the name is required in the New Institution Dialog, all other fields "
#| "are optional. As with the personal information dialog, this data is not "
#| "currently used by &kappname;, but will be required by future releases for "
#| "certain features. In particular, the Routing Number and the "
#| "<acronym><ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_9362\">BIC (Bank "
#| "Identifier Code)</ulink></acronym> will be required for online banking."
msgid ""
"Only the name is required in the New Institution Dialog, all other fields "
"are optional. As with the personal information dialog, this data is not "
"currently used by &kmymoney;, but some items may be required by future "
"releases for certain features. In particular, the <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Bank_code\">Bank Code</ulink> and the <acronym> <ulink "
"url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_9362\">BIC (Bank Identifier Code)</"
"ulink></acronym> will be required for online banking, although this may "
"depend on the country your bank is in."
msgstr ""
"Samo je ime potrebno u Dijalogu Nove Institucije, sva ostala polja su "
"opcionalna. Kao sa dijalogom ličnih informacija, ovi podaci se trenutno ne "
"koriste od strane &kappname;, ali će biti potrebni za buduću izdanja "
"određenih opcija. Npr., Broj Usmjeravanja i <acronym><ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_9362\">BIC (Bank Identifier Code - kod za "
"identificiranje banke)</ulink></acronym> će biti potrebni za internet "
"bankarstvo."

